{"tid":2517526,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"馬道立：港區國安法最重要是法例如何實踐 香港近乎所有案件是公開予公眾","createTime":"2021-05-05T11:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T11:19:49.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1a1a558d975f4f0cff33e9a2546a624b3f647d6f","tid":2517526,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T11:12:34.000Z","msg":"終審法院前首席法官馬道立在網上研討會，討論到港區國安法賦權國安公署在特殊情況下介入案件對法治的影響，他指不能聚焦單一條文評論，最重要是法例最終如何實踐。<br />\n<br />\n馬道立：「港區國安法中，有要求到需重視及關注基本法，包括我們提及事項，亦要具體參考人權及自由部分，最終會如何實行？而不是聚焦於一或兩項條文，然後估計最壞的情境發生何事，審訊是否閉門進行，有沒有人可以知悉審訊情況，而在香港，近乎所有案件是公開予公眾。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=433701\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D433701&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn%2FLVWyXx0XMfrvcdwhNvS5Y%3D&h=cc7b5111\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D433701&h=853e7121\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=433701</a>"},{"pid":"3d3db49cf3fcd2ace8ec861059ad3e96778d471b","tid":2517526,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T11:13:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">好撚正義，當我白癡！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5ddc3faafb9a7b3d87ee69800d43585107056a23","tid":2517526,"uid":26770,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T11:14:37.000Z","msg":"當日我屌馬道立涉政治迫害,成班打手抹黑我<br />\n呢個咪就真相"},{"pid":"d5afd274fb6b2ecf8d94a63e6ae6f4f8c87f70ec","tid":2517526,"uid":37869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T11:15:39.000Z","msg":"中國近乎所有案件都係公開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ec7d58157e9b37060d8dea6ff67e8ddc330934","tid":2517526,"uid":62318,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score"